com.upsight.android.marketing

Interface UpsightBillboardManager

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    UpsightMarketingApi

    public interface UpsightBillboardManager
    Manager that handles Billboard objects.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean registerBillboard(Billboard billboard)
      Registers a Billboard with the UpsightBillboardManager.
      boolean unregisterBillboard(Billboard billboard)
      Unregisters a Billboard with the UpsightBillboardManager.

    • Method Detail

      • registerBillboard

        boolean registerBillboard(Billboard billboard)
        Registers a Billboard with the UpsightBillboardManager.
        Parameters:
        billboard - The Billboard.
        Returns:
        true if successful; false indicates a failure, which happens when an active Billboard with the same scope is already registered.

      • unregisterBillboard

        boolean unregisterBillboard(Billboard billboard)
        Unregisters a Billboard with the UpsightBillboardManager. You can only unregister a Billboard that hasn't been attached to any marketing content, since it is automatically unregistered when content is attached.
        Parameters:
        billboard - The Billboard.
        Returns:
        true if successful; false indicates a failure, which happens either when the Billboard is not already registered.
